;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.2k</span></span></a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/obetomuniz/awesome-webcomponents\">awesome-webcomponents</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/obetomuniz/awesome-webcomponents\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">348</span></span></a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/afonsopacifer/awesome-flexbox\">awesome-flexbox</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/afonsopacifer/awesome-flexbox\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.1k</span></span></a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>Please read the <a href=\"https://github.com/brunopulis/awesome-a11y/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">contribution guidelines</a> before contributing.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/brunopulis/awesome-a11y/blob/master/topics/newsletter.md\">Accessibility Weekly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/brunopulis/awesome-a11y/blob/master/topics/article